<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#spawn_link/1"><code class="inline">spawn_link</code></a> BIFs.</p></div>

    </div>


      <div class="summary-row">
        <div class="summary-signature">
          <a href="#spawn_opt/3" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">spawn_opt(Node, Fun, SpawnOpts)</a>
