      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#spawn_opt/5" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">spawn_opt(Node, Module, Function, Args, SpawnOpts)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Spawns a new process and initializes it as described in the beginning of this
manual page. The process is spawned using the
<a href="../../../../lib/../erts/doc/html/erlang.html#spawn_opt/2"><code class="inline">erlang:spawn_opt</code></a> BIFs.</p></div>

