      </div>

    <div class="summary-row">
      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#start/5" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">start(Module, Function, Args, Time, SpawnOpts)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Starts a new process synchronously. Spawns the process and waits for it to
start.</p></div>

    </div>


      <div class="summary-row">
        <div class="summary-signature">
          <a href="#start_link/4" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">start_link(Module, Function, Args, Time)</a>
        </div>
