      <div class="summary-signature">
        <a href="#start_link/5" data-no-tooltip="" translate="no">start_link(Module, Function, Args, Time, SpawnOpts)</a>

      </div>

        <div class="summary-synopsis"><p>Starts a new process synchronously. Spawns the process and waits for it to
start. A link is atomically set on the newly spawned process.</p></div>

    </div>


      <div class="summary-row">
        <div class="summary-signature">
